<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Air Point Redemption Rejection</title>
    <style>
        /* Header styling */
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green branding color */
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Airline Name</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Dear <%= recipientName %>,</p>

    <p>We regret to inform you that your <%= airPointType %> request has been rejected due to the following reasons:</p>

    <p>
        <% reasons.forEach((reason, index) => { %>
            <%= reason %><%= index !== reasons.length - 1 ? ', ' : '' %>
        <% }); %>
    </p>

    <p>Please review your account status and criteria for redemption eligibility. Feel free to contact us for further assistance.</p>

    <p>Sincerely,<br>
    [Your Airline's Name]</p>
</body>
</html>
